---
title: Balsamic Cherry-Glazed Beef Brisket & Mash with Nutty Greens & Parmesan-Roasted Veggies
description: Food has a special power to bring people together, we’ve all heard it before but when you lay out this feast you’ll see how true it is. The dark balsamic cherry glaze will catch everyone’s attention at the table when slicing into the beef brisket, so sit down and enjoy a spread that’s sure to be the hot topic of discussion at the table.
